data.description: Great home with a relaxing backyard and in ground pool! 4 bedrooms, 2 & 1/2 bathrooms, big pool with a nice recreational area, large fenced in backyard, and a detached workshop. The back deck is composite. It has an amazing sunroom that overlooks the pool for lounging around on game day or enjoying a pool party. The laundry room connects the owner suite and owner bathroom, with plenty of closet space, access to outside, with a utility sink, and 80 gallon water heater. Roof - 2021, Pool liner - 2021, Pool pump - 2023. Neighbors are friendly and home is minutes from the shops in Hartselle.
